  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Build a Free Primary School in Nairobi Slums</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We are building a high standard modern Container primary school suitable for an informal settlement (slum) in Githogoro, Nairobi, Kenya - to provide high quality education for needy families living below $365 per year. Our aim is to give free access to education for children who otherwise have no education, so they can break out of the vicious cycle of extreme poverty. Since 2005 we have given access to education for over 1,000 children from the slum and we want to increase the number to 3,000.</narrative>
  </description>
